text: Tomás Bernardo Domínguez Taunton (born 14 February 1986 in Mexico City) is a former Mexican professional footballer. He last played as a midfielder for Correcaminos UAT in the Liga de Ascenso. Domínguez formerly played in Liga MX with Atlante, making his top-level debut on 23 February 2008 against Tigres UANL.MedioTiempo. "Tomás Bernardo Domínguez - Atlante".
